            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div id="main">
      
    <div data-post-hero="fullwidth-image">

    <div data-post-hero-content="">
          

      

        <p>A look at some of the work that went into one of the coolest-looking video games in recent memory</p>

        
    </div>

      <figure>
          <picture>
  <source srcset="https://storage.ghost.io/c/30/f5/30f5b1bb-84ee-4c26-b446-fb9a5e512994/content/images/size/w320/format/webp/2026/06/destop.jpg 320w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/30/f5/30f5b1bb-84ee-4c26-b446-fb9a5e512994/content/images/size/w640/format/webp/2026/06/destop.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/30/f5/30f5b1bb-84ee-4c26-b446-fb9a5e512994/content/images/size/w960/format/webp/2026/06/destop.jpg 960w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/30/f5/30f5b1bb-84ee-4c26-b446-fb9a5e512994/content/images/size/w1280/format/webp/2026/06/destop.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1023px) 90vw, 1200px" type="image/webp">
  
</picture>
        <figcaption><span>Image: </span><a href="https://www.artstation.com/patrickbloom" rel="noreferrer"><span>Patrick Bloom</span></a></figcaption>
      </figure>

  </div>

<div data-post-date-group="" data-post-info="">
      <p><span>Published:</span>
        <time datetime="2026-06-19T06:44:46">June 19, 2026, 6:44 pm</time>
      </p>
        <p><i role="presentation">
  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path d="M6 6v6a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h10l-4 -4m0 8l4 -4"></path></svg>
</i>          <span>Last updated:</span>
          <time datetime="2026-06-20T01:46:59">June 20, 2026, 1:46 am</time>
        </p>
    </div>
    <article>
      <p>Despite coming out <a href="https://aftermath.site/marathon-bungie-soundtrack-ryan-lott/" rel="noreferrer">a few months back now</a> (March to be precise), Bungie has kept the artwork that went into <a href="https://aftermath.site/marathon-satire-readergrev/" rel="noreferrer"><em>Marathon's</em> creation</a> and development mostly under wraps. Until yesterday.</p><p>Now, the shackles are off, and around the world, artists both internal (at Bungie) and external (contractors) are showing off the work they contributed to one of the coolest-looking video games in recent memory.</p><p>I thought I'd round up some of the best of it here in some galleries (click/tap on each image to expand!), but every artist credit will contain a link to their own site/portfolio so you can check out loads more once you're done.</p><h2 id="dima-goryainov"><a href="https://www.artstation.com/dgoryainov?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Dima Goryainov</a></h2><figure><div></div></figure><hr><h2 id="allan-parker"><a href="https://www.artstation.com/allan-p?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Allan Parker</a></h2><figure><div></div></figure><hr><h2 id="eric-pfeiffer"><a href="https://www.artstation.com/espfeiffer?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Eric Pfeiffer</a></h2><figure></figure><hr><h2 id="kejun-wang"><a href="https://www.artstation.com/kejun66?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Kejun Wang</a></h2><figure></figure><hr><h2 id="patrick-bloom"><a href="https://www.artstation.com/patrickbloom?ref=aftermath.site">Patrick Bloom</a></h2><figure><div></div></figure><hr><h2 id="sigurd-fernstrom"><a href="https://www.artstation.com/fernstrom?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Sigurd Fernstrom</a></h2><figure><div></div></figure><hr><h2 id="taylor-e-rose-shop"><a href="https://www.artstation.com/tahlwin?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Taylor E Rose</a> (<a href="https://tahl.win/shop?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Shop</a>)</h2><figure></figure><hr><h2 id="tobias-kwan"><a href="https://www.artstation.com/tobiaskwan?ref=aftermath.site">Tobias Kwan</a></h2><figure><div></div></figure><hr><h2 id="karakter"><a href="https://www.artstation.com/karakter?ref=aftermath.site">karakter</a></h2><figure><div></div></figure><hr><h2 id="west-studio"><a href="https://www.weststudio.com/?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">West Studio</a></h2><figure><div></div></figure><hr><h2 id="daniel-chavez"><a href="https://www.daniolart.com/?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Daniel Chavez</a></h2><figure><div></div></figure><hr><h2 id="molly-mclaughlin"><a href="https://www.mollyanneart.com/?ref=aftermath.site">Molly McLaughlin</a></h2><figure></figure><hr><div data-layout="immersive">
                    
